Let's send Mr. Yu first.

78
00:03:51,611 --> 00:03:53,092
Thank you for standing up for me.

79
00:03:53,611 --> 00:03:54,131
You're welcome.

80
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,130
I'm a professional
when it comes to disrespecting people.

81
00:03:56,131 --> 00:03:56,731
But,

82
00:03:56,731 --> 00:03:58,092
I'm not going home tonight.

83
00:03:58,184 --> 00:03:59,192
I have to go to the office.

84
00:03:59,192 --> 00:03:59,690
So

85
00:03:59,736 --> 00:04:01,016
it's more convenient to send you first.

86
00:04:09,291 --> 00:04:09,891
What's the matter?

87
00:04:12,252 --> 00:04:12,812
I love you.

88
00:04:19,752 --> 00:04:21,050
Thank you for not being angry at me.

89
00:04:23,368 --> 00:04:24,872
I'll keep a distance in the future.

90
00:04:25,892 --> 00:04:26,811
