could cause a wedge between us,

93
00:04:32,171 --> 00:04:33,731
then our relationship is too fragile.

94
00:04:34,731 --> 00:04:36,572
Besides, trust goes both ways.

95
00:04:37,251 --> 00:04:39,692
Just like how you let Xu Guanrui
send me home,

96
00:04:40,212 --> 00:04:41,291
I too, trust you.

97
00:04:43,811 --> 00:04:45,811
But I don't like it when you keep

98
00:04:45,811 --> 00:04:47,411
accommodating Zhang Qingya.

99
00:04:48,491 --> 00:04:49,212
Liang Daiwen,

100
00:04:49,692 --> 00:04:51,012
you're not obliged to be nice

101
00:04:51,012 --> 00:04:52,132
or owe anyone anything.

102
00:04:53,171 --> 00:04:54,332
So stop putting all the burden

103
00:04:54,332 --> 00:04:55,491
onto yourself.

104
00:04:56,012 --> 00:04:57,291
You're living your own life.

105
00:04:58,291 --> 00:04:59,611
You need to think more for yourself.

106
00:05:04,972 --> 00:05:05,572
Understood.

107
00:05:06,332 --> 00:05:07,851
I will think for us both moving forward.

108
00:05:08,092 --> 00:05:08,611
Guys.

109
00:05:08,811 --> 00:05:09,851
Guys, guys.

110
00:05:10,532 --> 00:05:12,411
Can you think for my sake first?

111
00:05:12,452 --> 00:05:13,491
I'm sitting right here, guys.

112
00:05:13,592 --> 00:05:15,816
Please go somewhere private
if you want to be lovey-dovey.

113
00:05:16,532 --> 00:05:17,851
What would you do without me?

114
00:05:17,851 --> 00:05:19,371
Geez, for goodness sake.

115
00:05:19,572 --> 00:05:21,251
Whatever you can't rely
on Zhang Qingya for,

116
00:05:21,251 --> 00:05:22,171
you can rely on me.

117
00:05:22,692 --> 00:05:23,132
Okay.

118
00:05:31,692 --> 00:05:33,811
Just drive, will you? I'm begging you.

119
00:05:44,572 --> 00:05:45,251
You should go.

120
00:05:45,772 --> 00:05:47,132
Mr. Yu is waiting in the car.

121
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,128
I'll go after I see you to your house.

122
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,488
I left a crack in the window for him.

123
00:05:50,972 --> 00:05:52,851
Is he a puppy that you left in the car?

124
00:05:55,811 --> 00:05:56,731
Whoopee!

125
00:07:22,811 --> 00:07:23,332
Liang.

126
00:07:25,251 --> 00:07:25,811
I'm

127
00:07:26,692 --> 00:07:27,892
sorry to you and Yi.

128
00:07:30,251 --> 00:07:30,972
I didn't think

129
00:07:31,656 --> 00:07:33,032
it would happen so suddenly.

130
00:07:34,212 --> 00:07:35,051
I had no choice

131
00:07:35,931 --> 00:07:37,171
but to come back.

132
00:07:41,892 --> 00:07:42,491
Meixia

133
