had signed an organ donation form

134
00:07:45,411 --> 00:07:46,731
before she passed.

135
00:07:49,452 --> 00:07:51,892
She didn't want Yi
to see her last moments.

136
00:07:54,851 --> 00:07:55,371
She asked me

137
00:07:56,611 --> 00:07:57,652
to bring her ashes back

138
00:07:59,532 --> 00:08:00,572
after the last rites.

139
00:08:06,371 --> 00:08:07,572
How did Mdm. Wang

140
00:08:11,892 --> 00:08:12,772
spend her last days?

141
00:08:16,892 --> 00:08:17,892
We only just set out

142
00:08:19,772 --> 00:08:20,491
when her condition

143
00:08:21,572 --> 00:08:22,532
rapidly deteriorated.

144
00:08:24,572 --> 00:08:25,332
At first,

145
00:08:26,212 --> 00:08:27,652
she could control it with medication.

146
00:08:29,572 --> 00:08:30,171
Later,

147
00:08:30,931 --> 00:08:32,572
she couldn't take it anymore

148
00:08:33,784 --> 00:08:35,560
and that's when
I took her to the hospital.

149
00:08:38,891 --> 00:08:39,572
Meixia

150
00:08:40,696 --> 00:08:41,544
kept stopping me

151
00:08:42,251 --> 00:08:43,412
from telling you guys.

152
00:08:46,424 --> 00:08:47,944
With having to keep up the secrecy,

153
00:08:49,452 --> 00:08:51,092
she and Yi missed the chance to have

154
00:08:52,891 --> 00:08:53,771
