155
00:09:00,812 --> 00:09:01,851
It happened too quickly.

156
00:09:45,525 --> 00:09:46,680
(Where is the Great Meixia?)

157
00:09:46,704 --> 00:09:50,400
(Mrs. Meixia, please reply.)

158
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:04,237
(- Tell me if you need money.
- Mom knows, my dear.)

159
00:10:04,238 --> 00:10:06,760
(I have enough money, don't worry.)

160
00:10:07,698 --> 00:10:09,829
(- Remember to take photos
- Sure thing. I'll send it to you later.)

161
00:10:09,830 --> 00:10:27,400
(- I want to see your couple photos with Mr. He.
- Alright, I know.)

162
00:10:28,125 --> 00:10:31,160
(Call rejected)

163
00:11:10,932 --> 00:11:12,092
Take me to my mom.

164
00:11:19,371 --> 00:11:19,812
Okay.

165
00:11:54,251 --> 00:11:56,972
I'm still waiting for you at home.

166
00:12:09,212 --> 00:12:11,572
How did you turn out like this?

167
00:12:36,332 --> 00:12:38,011
I'll take you home.

168
