(This is your mom's phone.)

174
00:15:04,491 --> 00:15:05,932
(She asked me to pass it to you.)

175
00:16:11,499 --> 00:16:14,203
(My dear, I'm leaving.)

176
00:16:18,242 --> 00:16:21,007
(To Gu Yi)

177
00:16:21,007 --> 00:16:22,680
(To Liang)

178
00:16:22,680 --> 00:16:25,369
(My dear, I'm leaving)

179
00:16:37,131 --> 00:16:37,851
My dear daughter.

180
00:16:39,212 --> 00:16:40,332
I'm in the hospital.

181
00:16:43,092 --> 00:16:45,371
(I wanted to video call you)

182
00:16:46,452 --> 00:16:48,131
(but I worried about scaring you.)

183
00:16:49,572 --> 00:16:50,292
(After some thought,)

184
00:16:51,251 --> 00:16:52,491
(I reckon this was the better way.)

185
00:16:54,172 --> 00:16:55,212
(I know)

186
00:16:56,212 --> 00:16:57,531
(that you want to come and see me.)

187
00:16:59,731 --> 00:17:01,052
(I want to see you too.)

188
00:17:03,412 --> 00:17:04,412
(But the fact is,)

189
00:17:05,372 --> 00:17:07,011
(I didn't have the courage to let you)

190
00:17:07,011 --> 00:17:08,132
(see me the way I am now.)

191
00:17:10,091 --> 00:17:11,331
(I want you to remember)

192
00:17:11,412 --> 00:17:13,372
(only the beautiful Great Meixia.)

193
00:17:15,291 --> 00:17:16,212
(For you to remember)

194
00:17:17,652 --> 00:17:19,612
(the Great Meixia that makes
a mean fried hairtail,)

195
00:17:21,811 --> 00:17:24,412
(the Great Meixia that exchanged
your dad with a television.)

196
00:17:25,932 --> 00:17:28,932
The Great Meixia that backed you up
when you were bullied.

197
00:17:30,091 --> 00:17:31,852
Not to forget the jovial, cheeky

198
00:17:32,051 --> 00:17:33,571
and happy-go-lucky Great Meixia.

199
00:17:35,091 --> 00:17:35,612
Also

200
00:17:36,291 --> 00:17:39,251
the Great Meixia
with a horrible taste in men.

201
00:17:42,051 --> 00:17:42,571
Remember this.

202
00:17:45,132 --> 00:17:47,571
I will forever be your Dear Meixia.

203
00:17:56,731 --> 00:17:57,491
Gu Yi.

204
00:17:59,412 --> 00:18:01,051
With your lousy temper,

205
00:18:01,811 --> 00:18:03,811
you should count yourself lucky
to be able to get

206
00:18:04,892 --> 00:18:05,692
a man like Liang.

207
00:18:09,011 --> 00:18:10,771
Aside from being a little quiet

208
00:18:11,372 --> 00:18:12,251
and slow,

209
00:18:13,212 --> 00:18:14,172
at the end of the day,

210
00:18:14,852 --> 00:18:17,051
he doesn't have major flaws.

211
00:18:17,731 --> 00:18:18,132
Am I right?

212
00:18:21,731 --> 00:18:23,011
I might be terrible

213
00:18:23,011 --> 00:18:24,652
at picking a man for myself,

214
00:18:26,412 --> 00:18:28,172
but I'm confident in helping

215
00:18:29,132 --> 00:18:30,291
my daughter pick hers.

216
00:18:32,892 --> 00:18:34,412
Nobody is perfect.

217
00:18:36,571 --> 00:18:37,852
Between two companions,

218
00:18:40,132 --> 00:18:41,571
what matters most is supporting

219
00:18:42,251 --> 00:18:43,251
and validating each other.

220
00:18:44,811 --> 00:18:45,771
You made the choice,

221
00:18:46,692 --> 00:18:47,612
so you have to cherish it.

222
00:18:48,852 --> 00:18:49,972
Simply put,

223
00:18:50,972 --> 00:18:53,491
a companion is your chosen family.

224
00:18:55,132 --> 00:18:56,212
Once you make the choice,

225
00:18:57,491 --> 00:18:58,612
you are responsible for them.

226
00:19:01,091 --> 00:19:01,771
Gu Yi.

227
00:19:04,491 --> 00:19:05,892
I want to thank you.

228
00:19:07,571 --> 00:19:09,612
Thank you for being so mature this time.

229
00:19:13,051 --> 00:19:13,892
Thank you

230
00:19:14,771 --> 00:19:16,412
for letting me go on a trip.

231
00:19:21,251 --> 00:19:22,011
My dear,

232
00:19:23,412 --> 00:19:25,132
when I'm gone,

233
00:19:26,771 --> 00:19:29,172
don't take me back to our hometown.

234
00:19:31,892 --> 00:19:33,051
Let He

235
00:19:33,452 --> 00:19:34,811
pour my ashes into the sea.

236
00:19:36,731 --> 00:19:37,531
Then,

237
00:19:38,771 --> 00:19:41,172
whenever you see the ocean,

238
00:19:43,051 --> 00:19:44,571
that's me by your side.

239
00:19:46,212 --> 00:19:46,892
When

240
00:19:47,172 --> 00:19:48,731
the wind blows over the water,

241
00:19:49,932 --> 00:19:51,972
that's me brushing your face,

242
00:19:52,972 --> 00:19:53,892
giving you a hug.

243
00:19:55,692 --> 00:19:56,892
When it rains,

244
00:19:59,852 --> 00:20:02,892
that's me helping to put out
your fiery temper.

245
00:20:05,011 --> 00:20:05,932
And when

246
00:20:06,972 --> 00:20:08,811
a rainbow appears after the rain,

247
00:20:10,091 --> 00:20:12,452
that's me looking down on you
from heaven.

248
00:20:14,892 --> 00:20:15,731
Anyway,

249
00:20:16,771 --> 00:20:18,331
whether I change

250
00:20:19,452 --> 00:20:20,571
into a flower,

251
00:20:21,251 --> 00:20:22,331
a tree,

252
00:20:23,531 --> 00:20:25,051
or a little star,

253
00:20:26,852 --> 00:20:28,412
I'll be there with you,

254
00:20:30,372 --> 00:20:31,491
always by your side.

255
00:20:37,699 --> 00:20:43,324
♪Twilight overtakes the sky
at the horizon♪

256
00:20:46,328 --> 00:20:47,304
My dear daughter,

257
00:20:49,972 --> 00:20:50,692
I love you.

258
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:57,400
♪Despite my hesitation,
I won't back off♪

259
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:03,800
♪How I wish for one more page
in our story♪

260
00:21:03,890 --> 00:21:04,488
I love you.

261
00:21:04,567 --> 00:21:07,285
♪Right at this moment, you pass by♪

262
00:21:07,895 --> 00:21:11,043
♪Filling every corner♪

263
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:17,470
♪Soothing all the worries♪

264
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:21,329
♪I have seen your eyes, crystal clear♪

265
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:24,408
♪With my reflection in them♪

266
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:27,892
♪One day, you will also bravely♪

267
00:21:28,320 --> 00:21:31,368
♪Overcome those rough patches♪

268
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:34,822
♪I guess one part of the story♪

269
00:21:35,398 --> 00:21:39,150
♪Meets its awakened moment♪

270
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:45,640
♪Can I love you more?♪

271
00:22:00,934 --> 00:22:06,332
♪Please answer me♪

272
