00:22:47,972 --> 00:22:49,412
No one is born with the skill.

281
00:22:49,652 --> 00:22:50,452
What the audience see

282
00:22:50,652 --> 00:22:51,491
is you, the person.

283
00:22:51,512 --> 00:22:53,320
They don't care
if your reading is any good.

284
00:22:53,384 --> 00:22:54,290
Just follow the script.

285
00:22:56,852 --> 00:22:57,652
Don't worry.

286
00:22:58,011 --> 00:22:59,771
You just have to do well on the shoot.

287
00:22:59,972 --> 00:23:00,652
As for the rest,

288
00:23:00,892 --> 00:23:02,531
Mr. Huang will smooth out
any wrinkles.

289
00:23:28,852 --> 00:23:29,531
Can you cut it?

290
00:23:30,172 --> 00:23:30,652
No.

291
00:23:32,251 --> 00:23:32,932
I'll teach you.

292
00:23:33,132 --> 00:23:33,491
Okay.

293
00:23:34,612 --> 00:23:35,251
Look here.

294
00:23:37,091 --> 00:23:38,172
Do it like this.

295
00:24:09,251 --> 00:24:11,212
Are you living in the editing room?

296
00:24:11,610 --> 00:24:12,712
This is only the rough cut.

297
00:24:12,852 --> 00:24:14,051
Is this really necessary?

298
00:24:21,091 --> 00:24:21,932
What?

299
00:24:22,372 --> 00:24:23,132
Is it

300
00:24:23,412 --> 00:24:24,932
a problem being a professional?

301
00:24:25,612 --> 00:24:26,569
Hey, you're not going

302
00:24:26,570 --> 00:24:27,599
to last very long like this.

303
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,560
I don't want you to die here.

304
00:24:28,811 --> 00:24:30,331
You better not make me fire you.

305
00:24:38,692 --> 00:24:39,972
Add more shots of this lady.

306
00:24:40,652 --> 00:24:42,771
Who knows where the director
found this piece of gem.

307
00:24:48,184 --> 00:24:50,280
Someone found her dirt on some
relationship program's forum.

308
00:24:50,280 --> 00:24:52,312
She's revealed to be the mistress
who cheated.

309
00:24:52,932 --> 00:24:54,771
The program's popularity
soared because of it.

310
00:24:55,212 --> 00:24:56,771
There are many more ugly comments too.

311
00:24:58,172 --> 00:25:00,811
But guests who go on the show
all have their dirty secrets.

312
00:25:00,972 --> 00:25:01,612
This lady

313
00:25:01,656 --> 00:25:02,856
only goes for the looks

314
00:25:02,872 --> 00:25:04,744
and coupled with her less
than savory reputation.

315
00:25:04,811 --> 00:25:07,571
It totally hit the jackpot
for viral content.

316
00:25:08,011 --> 00:25:10,212
It's top of the search trend
without having to try.

317
00:25:11,912 --> 00:25:13,650
You don't know her
or what really happened.

318
00:25:14,412 --> 00:25:15,531
So don't speak ill so easily.

319
00:25:16,731 --> 00:25:18,212
I'm not the one who started it.

320
00:25:18,892 --> 00:25:20,412
A colleague was at the recording studio.

321
00:25:20,731 --> 00:25:23,172
They saw her mixing with the investors.

322
00:25:23,592 --> 00:25:25,144
The production crew said it themselves.

323
00:25:25,291 --> 00:25:27,692
She gets around for shoots
in luxury cars.

324
00:25:29,132 --> 00:25:30,612
I don't suppose those are all hearsay?

325
00:25:42,531 --> 00:25:43,612
A pretty woman like her

326
00:25:43,892 --> 00:25:44,811
who wants to make it big?

327
00:25:45,624 --> 00:25:47,130
She has to have
some tricks up her sleeve.

328
00:25:47,544 --> 00:25:49,016
If she wanted a proper relationship,

329
00:25:49,448 --> 00:25:51,032
she wouldn't go on
a relationship program.

330
00:25:54,212 --> 00:25:54,932
I'm off.

331
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:23,546
(Yi, the Demonness
is about to go berserk)

332
00:26:36,491 --> 00:26:37,531
Call Gu Yi.

333
00:26:39,452 --> 00:26:40,051
I'll do it.

334
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:46,394
(Gu Yi)

335
00:26:52,852 --> 00:26:53,811
Gu Yi, where are you?

336
00:26:54,452 --> 00:26:55,852
Did you forget about the meeting today?

337
00:26:56,212 --> 00:26:57,531
Everybody is waiting for you.

338
00:26:57,731 --> 00:26:59,291
