339
00:26:59,531 --> 00:27:00,172
I'm not going.

340
00:27:01,212 --> 00:27:02,372
Are you for real?

341
00:27:02,852 --> 00:27:05,372
Who said you could miss work
when you didn't apply for leave?

342
00:27:06,132 --> 00:27:07,132
We're discussing topics today.

343
00:27:07,251 --> 00:27:08,612
Do you expect me to write for you?

344
00:27:09,491 --> 00:27:10,291
I'm quitting.

345
00:27:14,852 --> 00:27:15,571
Gu Yi.

346
00:27:16,491 --> 00:27:18,852
Are you being obnoxious
just because you're an editor now?

347
00:27:19,612 --> 00:27:21,132
Where's your sense of responsibility?

348
00:27:21,811 --> 00:27:23,571
I said I'm quitting, okay?

349
00:27:24,051 --> 00:27:25,892
Go on and take my spot as the editor.

350
00:27:25,892 --> 00:27:26,972
Stop calling me.

351
00:27:27,932 --> 00:27:28,372
Hello?

352
00:27:28,811 --> 00:27:29,291
Gu Yi.

353
00:27:31,051 --> 00:27:31,571
Gu Yi?

354
00:27:33,811 --> 00:27:34,491
Hello, Ms. Zhang.

355
00:27:38,051 --> 00:27:38,731
This is Liang Daiwen.

356
00:27:40,811 --> 00:27:41,652
We're sorry.

357
00:27:42,731 --> 00:27:43,852
Gu Yi

358
00:27:44,331 --> 00:27:45,372
