359
00:27:46,892 --> 00:27:47,852
Is it possible for her

360
00:27:48,452 --> 00:27:49,172
to take the day off?

361
00:27:50,852 --> 00:27:51,372
Okay.

362
00:27:58,291 --> 00:27:58,892
Ms. Zhang,

363
00:27:59,291 --> 00:28:00,249
how could you

364
00:28:00,250 --> 00:28:01,432
just let Gu Yi get away with it?

365
00:28:02,412 --> 00:28:03,251
When she's back,

366
00:28:03,731 --> 00:28:05,091
she can explain it herself.

367
00:28:05,692 --> 00:28:06,932
She said she's quitting.

368
00:28:07,771 --> 00:28:09,011
I'm sure you heard it, right?

369
00:28:09,320 --> 00:28:10,600
Continue with the meeting.

370
00:28:12,771 --> 00:28:14,452
Live and let live.

371
00:28:19,692 --> 00:28:20,331
Zhi,

372
00:28:21,372 --> 00:28:22,212
Gu Yi is on leave.

373
00:28:22,612 --> 00:28:24,331
You'll handle the article
she was supposed to do.

374
00:28:24,932 --> 00:28:26,212
Report back if it's too much for you.

375
00:28:26,376 --> 00:28:27,592
Don't let it affect the progress.

376
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:28,250
Got it.

377
00:28:30,571 --> 00:28:31,571
On to the next point.

378
00:28:36,932 --> 00:28:37,571
Gu Yi.

379
00:28:39,372 --> 00:28:40,212
You know,

380
00:28:40,771 --> 00:28:42,612
with your lousy temper,

381
00:28:43,491 --> 00:28:45,291
you should count yourself lucky
to be able to get

382
00:28:46,972 --> 00:28:48,251
a man like Liang.

383
00:28:50,172 --> 00:28:52,132
I have to say he is quite a find.

384
00:28:54,132 --> 00:28:57,051
I might be terrible
at picking a man for myself,

385
00:28:58,692 --> 00:29:00,571
(Flight Itinerary)
but I'm confident in helping

386
00:29:01,384 --> 00:29:03,200
(Thursday Donghai - Dalian)
my daughter pick hers.

387
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,920
(Liang Daiwen, Gu Yi)

388
00:29:06,132 --> 00:29:08,172
Aside from being a little quiet

389
00:29:09,011 --> 00:29:09,811
and slow...

390
00:29:52,331 --> 00:29:53,852
Here we go.

391
00:29:57,771 --> 00:29:59,291
Look how happy your dad is.

392
00:29:59,491 --> 00:30:01,652
He even brought out his treasured wine.

393
00:30:01,731 --> 00:30:02,892
